Available Tools: initiate_return | get_return_status | exchange_item | get_refund_status
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "order_id": "string", "item_id": "string", "reason": "string" }
Response Schema: { "return_id": "string", "status": "string", "refund_amount": number, "label_url": "string" }
---
Question: I need to return the wireless mouse (SKU-204) from order ORD-7788 because it is defective.
Call: { "func_call": "initiate_return", "order_id": "ORD-7788", "item_id": "SKU-204", "reason": "defective" }
Response: { "return_id": "RET-112233", "status": "approved", "refund_amount": 29.99, "label_url": "https://shipping.example.com/labels/RET-112233.pdf" }

